verses.verse: Give <S%H3051><s%> unto the Lord <S%H3068><s%>, O you mighty <S%H1121><s%>, give <S%H3051><s%> unto the Lord <S%H3068><s%> glory <S%H3519><s%> and strength <S%H5797><s%>.

Give <S%H3051><s%> unto the Lord <S%H3068><s%> the glory <S%H3519><s%> due unto his name <S%H8034><s%>; worship <S%H7812><s%> the Lord <S%H3068><s%> in the beauty <S%H1927><s%> of holiness <S%H6944><s%>.

The voice <S%H6963><s%> of the Lord <S%H3068><s%> is upon the waters <S%H4325><s%>: the God <S%H410><s%> of glory <S%H3519><s%> thunders <S%H7481><s%>: the Lord <S%H3068><s%> is upon many <S%H7227><s%> waters <S%H4325><s%>.
The voice <S%H6963><s%> of the Lord <S%H3068><s%> is powerful <S%H3581><s%>; the voice <S%H6963><s%> of the Lord <S%H3068><s%> is full of majesty <S%H1926><s%>.
The voice <S%H6963><s%> of the Lord <S%H3068><s%> breaks <S%H7665><s%> the cedars <S%H730><s%>; Yes <S%H3068><s%>, the Lord breaks <S%H7665><s%> the cedars <S%H730><s%> of Lebanon <S%H3844><s%>.
He makes them also to skip <S%H7540><s%> like a calf <S%H5695><s%>; Lebanon <S%H3844><s%> and Sirion <S%H8303><s%> like a young <S%H1121><s%> unicorn <S%H7214><s%>.
The voice <S%H6963><s%> of the Lord <S%H3068><s%> divides <S%H2672><s%> the flames <S%H3852><s%> of fire <S%H784><s%>.
The voice <S%H6963><s%> of the Lord <S%H3068><s%> shakes <S%H2342><s%> the wilderness <S%H4057><s%>; the Lord <S%H3068><s%> shakes <S%H2342><s%> the wilderness <S%H4057><s%> of Kadesh <S%H6946><s%>.

The voice <S%H6963><s%> of the Lord <S%H3068><s%> makes the deer <S%H355><s%> calve <S%H2342><s%>, and discovers <S%H2834><s%> the forests <S%H3295><s%>: and in his temple <S%H1964><s%> does every one speak <S%H559><s%> of his glory <S%H3519><s%>.
The Lord <S%H3068><s%> sits <S%H3427><s%> upon the flood <S%H3999><s%>; Yes <S%H3068><s%>, the Lord sits <S%H3427><s%> King <S%H4428><s%> for ever <S%H5769><s%>.
The Lord <S%H3068><s%> will give <S%H5414><s%> strength <S%H5797><s%> unto his people <S%H5971><s%>; the Lord <S%H3068><s%> will bless <S%H1288><s%> his people <S%H5971><s%> with peace <S%H7965><s%>.
